sentence: It's  just  before  15:00  in  Gaza  and  Israel  (13:00  GMT)  and  here  are  some  of  the  latest  lines:  Israeli  forces  carried  out  an  intense  bombardment  in  the  southern  Gazan  city  of  Rafah  overnight  ,  which  according  to  the  Hamas-run  health  ministry  killed  at  least  67  Palestinians.
Across  The  Strip,  the  ministry  says  164  people  were  killed  in  the  last  day  -  bringing  the  total  number  of  people  killed  in  Gaza  to  more  than  28,100  .
